Modification Note (by Delta University Graduation Team, 2025):

This project was originally structured by Owonubi Job Sunday (2020).  
Substantial modifications have been made by a student team from Delta University (2025), including:

- Addition of enhanced validation checks.  
- Implementation of QR code generation for each student and its use in attendance logging.  
- Fixes for issues related to user deletion in the database.  
- Integration of dark mode.  
- Redesign of the overall theme and the login screen.

This modified version was developed as a graduation project to obtain a Bachelor's degree  
in Management Information Systems. The contributing team members are:

